<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <title>Payment Failed Notification</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
      .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; } .header { text-align: center; padding: 10px
      0; } .content { padding: 20px 0; } .button { background-color: #d9534f;
      color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius:
      5px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h2>Payment Failed Notification</h2>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
        <p>We’re reaching out to inform you that the payment for your order
          (Order No.
          {{orderNo}}) on
          {{orderDate}}
          was unsuccessful.</p>
        <p><strong>Order Details:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>Plan: {{planName}}</li>
          <li>Plan Price: ${{planPrice}}</li>
          <li>Total Amount: ${{totalAmount}}</li>
          <li>Delivery Option: {{deliveryOption}}</li>
          <li>Promo Code: {{promoCode}}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If you’d like to try the payment again or if you have questions,
          please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing Life Agent Portal. We appreciate your business
          and look forward to helping you.</p>
      </div>
      <footer>
        <p>If you received this email by mistake or have any questions, please
          contact our support team.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>